    dc:description "FIGURE 27. A) Mecyna subsequalis (Herrich-Schäffer), female, West Azarbaijan, Orumiyeh. B, C) Nomophila noctuella (Denis & Schifferm̧ller), male, Kerman, Fariab (B), and male, Tehran, Evin (C). D) Elbursia stocki Amsel, male. C) Mukia nigroanalis Amsel, male. D) Iranomecyna dimorphalis Amsel, male (scale bar = 10.0 mm)." ;
